  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Aged between 19 and 75 years

          -  Signed informed consent

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  At screening, SPB ≥ 180mmHg or DBP ≥ 110mmHg or LDL-C &gt; 250mg/dL or TG ≥ 400mg/dL

          -  Has a history of hypersensitivity to Angiotensin Ⅱ receptor blocker or HMG-CoA
             reductase inhibitor or component of this drug

          -  Has a history of multi-drug allergy
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
